reviewText: Great fun for those who would like to get under Sinatra's skin, be THE VOICE for just an hour, and you will keep repeating those hours. Fabulous also for parties, just play the disk and 8 out of 10 men (women tend to be more modest about their vocal qualities) will start balking. To stimulate interaction this is a great tool, and to remind you of how exceptional Sinatra really was. For Sinatra fans this is a must-have!!
